item.title: SoftLayer_Software_Component_HostIps_Mcafee_Epo_Version45_Hips_Version7
item.description: SoftLayer_Software_Component_HostIps_Mcafee_Epo_Version45_Hips_Version7 Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Software_Component_HostIps_Mcafee_Epo_Version45_Hips_Version7 data type represents a single McAfee Secure Host IPS software component for version 7 of the Host IPS client and uses the ePolicy Orchestrator version 4.5 backend. Local epoVersion The version of ePolicy Orchestrator that the host IPS client communicates with. Type: string hardwareId Hardware Identification Number for the server this Software Component is installed upon. Type: integer
